    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "openclaw_detail",
      "x": 545, "y": 170,
      "width": 390, "height": 110,
      "text": "AI Agents (Bjorn, etc.)\n  \u2514\u2500 Autonomous task execution via Claude/GPT\n\nOpenClaw Gateway (WebSocket + HTTP)\n  \u2514\u2500 LiteLLM model routing, session management\n\nWorkspace API (port 3939)\n  \u2514\u2500 Session files, chat history, agent state",
      "originalText": "AI Agents (Bjorn, etc.)\n  \u2514\u2500 Autonomous task execution via Claude/GPT\n\nOpenClaw Gateway (WebSocket + HTTP)\n  \u2514\u2500 LiteLLM model routing, session management\n\nWorkspace API (port 3939)\n  \u2514\u2500 Session files, chat history, agent state",
      "fontSize": 11,
      "fontFamily": 3,
